Class WorkManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.drill.exec.work.WorkManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable

    public class WorkManager
extends Object
implements AutoCloseable
    Manages the running fragments in a Drillbit. Periodically requests run-time stats updates from fragments running elsewhere.
